## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **filgrastim Neupogen 1991** = first FDA G-CSF chemo-induced neutropenia. 35년 표준. quantum-VQE 의 G-CSF receptor 결합 (homodimer + JAK2/STAT5 활성) 가 직접 fit.
2. **pegfilgrastim Neulasta 2002** = PEGylated long-acting G-CSF — once-per-cycle. PEG + protein 결합 = quantum-VQE 의 PEG-protein interface modeling 한정.
3. **eflapegrastim Rolontis 2022** = first 한국 단백질 신약 FDA G-CSF (한미약품). SAFA (Succinyl-Adamantane Fatty Acid) scaffold = WEAVE axis 의 K-novel scaffold.
4. **ondansetron Zofran 1991** = first FDA 5-HT3 antagonist CINV — cisplatin acute emesis paradigm shift. 35년 표준. quantum-VQE 의 5-HT3 ion channel pocket fit.
5. **aprepitant Emend 2003** = first FDA NK1 antagonist — delayed CINV. ondansetron + dexamethasone + aprepitant triple combo = NCCN 1L. quantum-VQE 의 NK1 GPCR pocket fit.
6. **olanzapine 5-mg antiemetic NCCN 1L** = atypical antipsychotic (5-HT2A/D2/H1) repurposed antiemetic. cross-psychiatric + eating_disorders. 만성 best-cost-effectiveness 적응증 외 처방.
7. **palifermin Kepivance 2004** = first FDA KGF (KGFR/FGFR2b agonist) chemo + RT mucositis. HSCT high-dose conditioning grade 3-4 mucositis 단축. quantum-VQE 의 KGFR (FGFR2b splice variant) pocket fit. cross-newborn_perinatal 일부 KGF cross.
8. **anamorelin JP 2021** = first GHSR1a agonist NSCLC cachexia. 일본 단독 승인 (FDA + EMA reject 2017). cross-eating_disorders + palliative_care. quantum-VQE 의 GHSR1a GPCR pocket fit.
9. **duloxetine 2010 CIPN guideline 1L** = SNRI repurposed CIPN — ASCO + ESMO guideline 1L. 만성 cisplatin + 만성 oxaliplatin + 만성 paclitaxel 후 6개월+ 잔존 sensorimotor neuropathy. cross-pain.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, 만성 supportive care 임상 의미 한정.

